Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我国有许多被誉为名作的文学作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 或许不少人都感觉这些作品与自己无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对年轻人来说是过去的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对年长的人来说是过去看过的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今若重新执卷在手 定会为其感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公们或烦恼 或叹息 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或有蓬勃的朝气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其形象与现在的我们重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更充满了我们在现代生活中轻易忘却的可怜与生涩之感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如这本《人间失格》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文豪太宰治的代表作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发行量超过1千万本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本最广为人知的不朽名作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而这绝非陈年旧事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 人间失格第一话


Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生充满了耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 所谓人的生活实在难以捉摸

Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（昭和4年：1929年）

Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话 镰仓殉情

Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去探望丈夫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开店了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要判死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人叫真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名我后来才知道 似乎叫恒子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人说 是我杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 我参加了反社会运动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据内务省称 目前失业人员已逾10万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里失业的人与日俱增
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里卖身的人接连不断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接连不断…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我妹妹 也为了贴补家计
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫卖身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子才上初中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要革命 革命！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是打倒政府的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武装起义已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里签上名 参加我们的运动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要签名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请协助捐款购买武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这钱来得真是易如反掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 行动队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你演戏也很有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小丑一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是为穷人谋福利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却从更穷的人身上榨取钱财
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若知道这样的你其实是个大富豪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会作何感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊对您参加非法运动的事恼怒非常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这运动是为了社会进步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还在学习绘画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊说若您继续为他身为议员的面子抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就要断绝您的生活费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我也无法再袒护您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这不是最后一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若断绝生活费 我便只有死路一条了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把这话转告给我父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在原地不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特高 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}特高：特别高等警察\N大正到昭和前期日本主要府县警中设置的政治警察，受内务省直接指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来 从窗口逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 厕所查过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放长线钓大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人太显眼 在此分头行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捐款到底在谁手上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 借点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你家里给了生活费吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拿开 人看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是有吗 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱出钱 老规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生充满了耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去东京的高等学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}1950年以前的旧制高等学校相当于大学预科，与现代的高中不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想当个画家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 客人就一位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 我很寂寞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道家时髦的好店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我乡下的弟弟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我在这避一避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…这里来瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 假装客人是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}再来瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小菅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 您今天就收工了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 方便去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要待到几时啦


Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你让我避了风头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是特高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们这儿的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是耀武扬威的 我讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你一副惴惴不安的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现就糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作是情侣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这娼妇 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生充满了耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿叶 笑得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今依然搞不懂何谓人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:12:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是女人 完全是不可思议的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肌肤 仿佛有种令人怀念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是画具的味道吧 我在学画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那你会成为画家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那才华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不再去见我丈夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在服役
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世道 真受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你去搞革命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是参加了运动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动不过是装个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我根本没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为画没什么起色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而反社会的态度像是艺术家的派头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎 装什么坏人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分明很单纯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这世道有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的生活方式也不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人这种生物 为何总爱顺着自己的意解释事物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何对真相视而不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 我确实对这女人起了杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什么生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母跟我断绝了关系 没了资金来源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后立马走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生帽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素描簿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏呢 还是要书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅草的商店街有卖舞狮子用的狮子装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小正适合小孩子披在身上玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶藏还是喜欢书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把父亲惹恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来到浅草商店街 打开记事本一看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 这上面竟然写着“狮子舞”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是我的字迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叶藏的恶作剧哩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可真是个怪孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后才想要得不得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在玩具铺的店头忍不住哈哈大笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是耻辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不能再去店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…去死好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟朋友借的 还没还呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点困了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推我一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能活得像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快些来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还有气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快出船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在岩盘上的男人像是殉情的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崖上好像还有女人的腰带和草鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是能找到 说不定女的也还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉你父亲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊恼怒非常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是安眠药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要几片？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可真是个怪孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分明很单纯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不再去见丈夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快些来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说警部 真的是殉情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是呢喃着说是他杀了那女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听谁说的 别把风言风语往报纸上写
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 找到女的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 女的还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…

Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:30.78,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕たちは何かを
