Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.51,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遅く起きた朝でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:49.17,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日目を覚ますんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:23:01.67,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちょっとでも笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:07.86,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつだってこの世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:14.52,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが必要だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:30.78,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:37.37,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}究竟为了追寻什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:42.51,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}睡过头的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:49.17,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也日复一日地清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.77,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:55.34,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:23:01.67,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:07.86,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:14.52,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总是需要你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.70,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's not too late
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:19.61,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We say hello
